Life lately has been about the quieter kind of Joy, not showy , not always loud. Sometimes derived from seeing the smiles of others around me. From being present with my friends & colleagues; with nature , from newer experiences in strange cities . 
Not everything has made sense.
But everything has made me. 
And for that, i’m deeply, quietly grateful. 💗🙏🏻
